KWIK SNAX.
----------
DIZZY TO THE RESCUE!.OUTWIT ZAKS COURT JESTERS,BUMBLE BEES,CLOCKWORK MICE AND
MORE IN THE LAND.PERSONALITY,MEGA FEATURES AND FANTASTIC FUN IN THE INCREDIBLY
PLAYABLE ACTION PACKED ARCADE PUZZLE GAME!

DIZZY AND THE YOLKFOLK BAND HAD JUST FINISHED THEIR GRUELLING TOUR OF YOLKLAND
AND WHERE ALL READY FOR A HOLIDAY,UNFORTUNATELY COULD`NT DECIDE WHERE TO GO
AND A HUGE ARGUMENT BEGAN TO RAGE...I SAY UNFORTUNATELY BECAUSE IT WAS WITH
ZAKS THE EVIL WIZARD. HE GOT INTO A HUGE TEMPER AND CAST SPELLS LEFT RIGHT AND
CENTRE...

DENZIL     ; THOUGHT HE WAS SO COOL HE WENT TO ICELAND..
DYLAN      ; ALWAYS HAD HIS HEAD IN THE CLOUDS SO HE WENT TO CLOUDLAND
GRAND DIZZY; WAS GETTING A BIT OLD SO WENT TO CUCKOOLAND
DAISY      ; WAS TRAPPED IN ZAKS DARK DUNGEON 

DIZZY WENT WILD HE HAD TO GET THE YOLKFOLK BACK TOGETHER HE HAD FORGOTTEN TO
TELL THEM ABOUT THE FAREWELL GIG HE PLANNED DOWN AT THE LOCAL CLUB!..

THE GAME.
---------

THE GAME IS DIVIDED INTO 4 LEVELS,EACH MORE DEVASTING THAN THE LAST.POINT
DIZZYS GLOVE TO THE REQUIRED LEVEL AND PRESS FIRE.

WEAVE AROUND THE STATIONERY BLOCKS AND PUSH THE SLIDING ONES INTO THE
APPROACHING HENCHMEN TO GET THE FRUIT COMPLETE 5 LEVELS AND FREE A FRIEND.

THERE ARE SPECIAL FEATURES WHICH FLOAT DOWN TO HELP,BUT SOMETIMES THEY WILL
HINDER. A SPECIAL BONUS SCORE IS AWARDED WHEN YOU GET THE FRUIT IN FLASHING
ORDER.

AFTER EVERY LEVEL THERE IS A SPECIAL SLIPPERY SLIDY BONUS SECTION.WHEN DIZZY
STARTS IN A DIRECTION HE IS UNABLE TO STOP HE HITS SOMETHING - ITS THAT
SLIPPERY..PLAN YOUR MOVES WELL- THERE ARE`NT ANY HENCHMEN..BUT YOUR UP AGAINST
THE CLOCK.

...AND THATS THE END OF THE DIZZY COLLECTION...BUT THERE ARE THE THE DOX TO 2
MORE DIZZY GAMES FOLLOWING THIS...TYPED AGAIN BY SCOOTER/SKID ROW.............
